[section#exec.parschedrepl.general
    [:en] General
    [:zh_CN] 概述
]

[para]
[:en] Facilities in the [`parallel_scheduler_replacement] namespace
allow users to replace the default implementation of [`parallel_scheduler].
[:zh_CN] [`parallel_scheduler_replacement] 命名空间中的各项设施允许用户替换
[`parallel_scheduler] 的缺省实现。
